---
---

<section class="py-16 px-4">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Cómo son nuestras actividades</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-primary">
            <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
            <path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
            <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">Grupos pequeños</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">Máximo 8 personas por actividad</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-primary">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
            <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">Ritmo cómodo y accesible</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">Sin prisas ni exigencias físicas extremas</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-primary">
            <path d="M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">No se requiere experiencia previa</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">Te guiamos en todo momento</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-primary">
            <path d="M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 9.8 6.1C15.5 5 17 4.48 19 2c1 2 2 4.18 2 8 0 5.5-4.78 10-10 10Z"></path>
            <path d="M2 21c0-3 1.85-5.36 5.08-6C9.5 14.52 12 13 13 12"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">Ambiente relajado</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">Respetuoso con el entorno</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        El objetivo no es hacer más, sino <span class="font-semibold text-foreground">disfrutar mejor</span>: sin agobios, sin prisas y en buena compañía.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
